      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $u_n = \\sqrt{ n + \\sqrt{ n-1 + \\dots + \\sqrt 1 }}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n = \\sqrt{ n + \\sqrt{ n-1 + \\dots\n+ \\sqrt 1 }}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5a125c79-5775-4b19-b850-693d463ead04",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que la suite $\\left(\\frac{u_n}{\\sqrt n}\\right)$ est born{\\'e}e.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que la suite <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\left(\\frac{u_n}{\\sqrt n}\\right)\\)</span> est\nborn<span>é</span>e.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4145f128-39bf-429e-a9c4-35e32ecbb74a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Par r{\\'e}currence, $\\sqrt n \\le u_n \\le \\sqrt{2n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Par r<span>é</span>currence, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt n \\le\nu_n \\le \\sqrt{2n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c7089e66-ce2d-4853-b769-3d52cfa7e18f",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}terminer $\\lim_{n\\to\\infty} \\left(\\frac{u_n}{\\sqrt n}\\right)$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>terminer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{n\\to\\infty}\n\\left(\\frac{u_n}{\\sqrt n}\\right)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ed6c417f-9d0d-4bb3-a0bc-03382c81d702",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sqrt n \\le u_n \\le \\sqrt{n+\\sqrt{2(n-1)}}  \\Rightarrow  \\lim = 1$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt n \\le u_n \\le\n\\sqrt{n+\\sqrt{2(n-1)}}  \\Rightarrow  \\lim = 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1f26f98b-c356-43f2-ac18-6f74c701716b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}terminer $\\lim_{n\\to\\infty}(u_n-\\sqrt n\\,)$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>terminer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{n\\to\\infty}(u_n-\\sqrt n\\,)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "862d81d8-c1e7-451b-a104-6faa47aa1f18",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
