        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{n+\\sqrt{n-1}} \\le u_n \\le\n\\sqrt{n+\\sqrt{n-1+\\sqrt{2(n-2)}}}\n               \\Rightarrow  \\lim = \\frac 12\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
